snippet.textDisplay:
New generation will never understand what it feels to grow with a childhood full of Ustad NFAK, Junaid Jamshed/TheVitalSigns, Madam Noor Jehan, Junoon, Alamgir era, Nazia-Zoheb etc followed by a teenage era filled with EP, MKH, Strings, Fuzon, Roxen, Call, Jal, Atif Aslam etc etc
and then a huge dissapointing downfall of Pakistani music from 2007- onwards followed by shitty bollywood music takeover.
